org.jsonurl.text

Class JsonUrlTextAppender<A extends Appendable,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsonurl.text.JsonUrlTextAppender<A,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - Accumulator type
    R - Result type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Appendable, JsonUrlOptionable, JsonTextAppendable<A,R>, JsonTextBuilder<R>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonUrlStringBuilder

    public abstract class JsonUrlTextAppender<A extends Appendable,R>
extends Object
implements JsonTextAppendable<A,R>, JsonUrlOptionable
    A JsonTextAppendable that appends JSON→URL text to any Appendable.

    Note, like StringBuilder an instance of this class is not thread-safe.

    Since:
    2019-09-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
